Now a #1 Bestseller on Amazon in Vegetarian Cooking, Superfood Recipes, and Health and Wellness

Everywhere, people are raving about these 99 amazing recipes proven to help you achieve your ultimate health...

Don't just discover the power of superfoods, use the power of superfoods and be amazed at just how tasty "healthy" can be!

This collection of 99 recipes covers everything, from slow cooker soups, green smoothies and salads to Friday night dinners and dessert. Every recipe in this book includes not just one, but several superfoods, making them incredibly nutritious and showing just how simple it can be to make healthy choices for every meal of the day.
